John Tate (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Tate_(actor) 0 John Tate (1915–79) was an Australian actor. He was the father of Nick Tate and was married to Neva Carr Glynn. He divorced Glynn in 1954.After appearing in On the Beach (1959) he moved to England where he lived the rest of his life. John_Tate ( 1915 – 79 ) was an_Australian_actor . He was the_father of Nick_Tate and was_married to Neva_Carr_Glynn . He divorced Glynn in 1954 . After appearing in On the_Beach_(_1959 ) he moved to England where he lived the_rest of his_life .
